Description:
Great Entertaining Home
Upon entering the home, you have a formal loungeroom to the left of the house, also at the front of the home is the master bedroom with walk in robe and ensuite. Open plan kitchen, dining and family area which has a sliding door out to a paved area for those sunny days to enjoy a meal or a coffee. Loads of cupboards and bench space in the kitchen, stainless steel appliances including Dishlex dishwasher, 900mm electric oven with gas cooktop and rangehood. At the rear of the home is large laundry and linen cupboard. Main bathroom which has the shower over the spa bath IXL tastic. Second and third bedrooms both with built in robes. Evaporative cooling and ducted heating throughout. Internal access to the double lock up garage, security system, large under cover alfresco area covered with the beautiful vines. Garden shed, 18,000 litre water tank and solar panels on the home all of which sits on a block size of 729sqm (approx.) With only 5 minutes from Bellarine Village & Newcomb Central Shopping Centre, dont forget East Geelongs cafes and shops. 10 minutes from Geelong CBD, Hospitals, Eastern Park Gardens and the Waterfront. Inspection a must!

Description:
Living Large in Fabulous Central Location!!
With a sought after location and not a thing to do at this fantastic residence, it's sure to be at the top of your shopping list! Only four years old and offering four bedrooms, three living areas and three bathrooms, this stylish home will easily cater for the whole family but also perfect for professionals wanting a fabulous location on the doorstep of the CBD and Eastern Park.
A private yet chic façade offering great street appeal and manicured gardens upon entry is just the start, what's beyond the orange door is sure to exceed your expectations!
The floor plan of the home has been drafted carefully to offer practical everyday living, upon entry to the ground level you are greeted with neutral tones, Tasmanian oak timber floors and high ceilings. A study and 1st bedroom with walk in robe oversee the front of the home which then flows to the first living area and combined laundry/1st bathroom. The heart of the home is the light filled open plan kitchen/meals area with fantastic aluminum stacking doors that open up onto the entertainment decked area complete with a trendy electric awning. The designer kitchen will please the enthusiastic cook with stone bench tops, 900 gas cooktop/electric oven, pot drawers, butler's pantry with dishwasher, large plumbed fridge provision, 2nd sink and ample cupboard space.
Make your way up the hardwood stairs where you will find the shrewdly designed master bedroom with own private balcony, walk in robe and ensuite with double vanity, toilet and double shower. A comfortable 2nd living area divides the master bedroom and the remaining bedrooms both with built in robes and zoned 3rd bathroom with bath, shower and toilet.
The yard has been fully landscaped in a low maintenance fashion for your convenience, the decked area has been designed for entertaining, built-in seating is featured so there is always enough space to gather around the built in, plumbed BBQ.
Features include evaporative cooling, central heating, premium gas log fire, ducted vacuum, stone bench tops throughout the home, hardwood floors, block out/sheer blinds, plenty of storage cavities, 2 access points to the yard, aggregate concrete, double lock up garage with remote entry and R.O.W lane access.
This home has been completed with excellent craftsmanship and high end finishes, a perfect fusion of lifestyle and low maintenance living with a versatile floor plan offering practicality and spacious rooms throughout.

Description:
Impressive weatherboard home with the potential for development
This impressive weatherboard, 4 bed, 2 bath, 2 living, 60's built home set on approximately 685m2 features side access, original hardwood flooring and is freshly painted throughout. In close proximity to Geelong's CBD, the Botanic Gardens & Waterfront district. This charming home would suit a family, developer (STCA with side access) or keen investor with a potential rent of $380 - $400pw.
Comprising of a neat entry and front formal living room filled with natural light and split system heating/cooling. A second living area which is the hub of the home has a unique warm and cozy feel featuring a Regency gas fire heater.
Down the 9-meter hallway you will find 4 bedrooms to the left. The front bedroom includes a BIR and a large window looking out onto the green lawn. Rooms 2 and 3 include storage and double block out blinds. Bedroom 4 has block out blinds and has the potential to make a great nursery or study.
Next to the 4th bedroom you'll find the main bathroom featuring an updated vanity and shower/bath set up with a separate toilet. The 2nd bathroom/laundry has a toilet, newly fitted shower and heatlamps. This fantastic functional kitchen comprises of a Bosch dishwasher, great cupboard space, 4 burner gas cooktop with oven and seating for up to 6. Outdoors offers a large, low maintenance and secure, well fenced backyard including a paved area and lush green grass. This spacious area is would be perfect for children or your 4 legged friend and would appeal to developers with a large rear yard and wide side access (STCA). This fantastic property is close to public transport and a short stroll from the Newcomb Shopping Centers, numerous Primary and Secondary schools, 15-minute drive to the Bellarine Peninsula and only 3km to the Geelong CBD.
FEATURES
- Gas fire heater
- Split system heating and cooling
- 685m2 approx with side access
- Potential Rent $380pw - $400pw
- 2 Living spaces

Address: 1-3 Newhaven Avenue St Albans Park VIC 3219
Description:
Double Garage Plus Parking Bay for Caravan or Boat
This exceptional residence sits on the perfect allotment for those that enjoy that lovely feeling of open space with the home featuring 2 street frontages, a grassy reserve down the 3rd side and only one neighbour at the rear of the property. All this open space allows a striking tranquil view over the neighbouring farm land providing a quiet, peaceful setting. Boasts a separate secure parking bay with outward swinging gates that is ideal for storing a large caravan, boat or trailer and with direct excess to the street reversing and parking is a breeze.
The home comprises 4 bedrooms, the master bedroom with a luxury ensuite, walk in robe and a private timber decked courtyard, whilst all 3 additional bedrooms are well sized and with built-in robes. Delightful formal sitting room or home office, stunning gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry and an abundance of cupboard and bench space. Large open plan sundrenched north facing family room, with large siding door access to a sensational covered outdoor living area, the perfect setting for large scale entertaining. On the outside a private north facing rear yard, double garage with remote control door and the security of internal access completes this exquisite home.

Description:
Best value in the market today.
Meticulously maintained and immaculately presented, this property offers incredible value for the first home buyer looking for an affordable entry into the market, a savvy investor looking for a low maintenance investment with solid returns or the downsizer looking for a quiet setting and a home with little to do.
Positioned in a low traffic established street, the location offers an element of
peace without sacrificing on proximity to amenities with public transport at the end of the street and a number of schools for all levels and multiple shopping centres all within a few minutes.
Internally, the home has been recently carpeted and painted and comprises 2 generously proportioned bedrooms with built in robes, central bathroom, open kitchen / meals area, living, separate laundry and separate toilet. Reverse cycle airconditioning and ceiling fans in every room control the climate year round.
Outside, a north facing courtyard gives you a private space to entertain, the large front yard is established and low maintenance and a single lock up garage provides secure off street parking.
To take advantage of this opportunity, call Dion to learn more on 0424 940 629.
